<lb />3) a single step of gradual process: <cit><quote>supplying every s. with an augmented greeting,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 3.6.54" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 6, 54</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to learn of me the --s of our story,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 4.4.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 4, 9</bibl></cit>.
